<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10700>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Hibiscadelphus stellatus. A Habit B Flowers and leaves (from the holotype) C View of bracts illustrating stellate arrangement D Close-up of flower. (from the holotype). All photos by the authors." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10700" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10701>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Hibiscadelphus stellatus H. Oppenh., Bustamente, & Perlman. A Habit B Flower bud C Surface of calyx showing stellate hairs D Flower E Surface of corolla showing two sizes of stellate hairs F Fruit G Longitudinal section of fruit showing seed. Drawn from Oppenheimer et al. H 41337 (US) and field photographs by the authors." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10701" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10702>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Distribution map showing known locations of Hibiscadelphus stellatus on West Maui." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10702" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

